1. Junction discovery saturates at step 1000 (~21/65 found)
2. Silicon runs out late game (377→80) — fewest extractors (45 vs 50-58)
3. Clips overtakes us: friendly 21→12, enemy 0→13 (steps 1000→5000)
4. Miners mine wrong resource (can't find silicon extractors)
